# Firmware
## [http://downloads.canaan-creative.com/software/avalon2/2014-01-23/  20140123]

* Include the first stable version of MM firmware
* Include the RPi OpenWrt firmware with LUCI web UI configure/status page
* Support static Fan speed
* Display all modulars status include 2 fan, 2 temperature sensors, voltage and frequency
* Voltage display as encode mode. needs to be changed to human readable
* Upload the ASIC cores testing script file

